languages.text: "Будь проклята наследница Тисифоны! Я знаю, однажды Дом Орселлио сбросит оковы тирана, пусть не сегодня и не здесь. Вслед за мной придут и другие — и пусть трепещут наши враги!"

traits.locale_text: "Будь проклята наследница Тисифоны! Я знаю, однажды Дом Орселлио сбросит оковы тирана, пусть не сегодня и не здесь. Вслед за мной придут и другие — и пусть трепещут наши враги!"
traits.speaker: NaviRadicalLeader

languages.text: "Tisiphone's heir be damned! I know that House Orsellio will cast off the tyrant's shackles someday, though not here and now. Others will come after me — and may our enemies tremble!"

languages.text: “愿上天诅咒提西福涅的继承人！我知道，即便不是现在，奥赛罗家族也总有一天会摆脱暴君的枷锁。其他人会为我报仇的，让我们的敌人颤抖吧！”
languages.original_text: "Tisiphone's heir be damned! I know that House Orsellio will cast off the tyrant's shackles someday, though not here and now. Others will come after me — and may our enemies tremble!"

traits.locale_text: “愿上天诅咒提西福涅的继承人！我知道，即便不是现在，奥塞罗家族也总有一天会摆脱暴君的枷锁。其他人会为我报仇的，让我们的敌人颤抖吧！”
traits.speaker: NaviRadicalLeader

languages.text: «¡Maldita sea la heredera de Tisiphone! Sé que algún día la casa Orsellio se librará del yugo de la tiranía, aunque no sea ni aquí ni ahora. Otros vendrán después de mí... ¡y nuestros enemigos temblarán!».
languages.original_text: "Tisiphone's heir be damned! I know that House Orsellio will cast off the tyrant's shackles someday, though not here and now. Others will come after me — and may our enemies tremble!"

traits.speaker: NaviRadicalLeader

languages.text: 「ティシフォンの後継なんて呪いよ！オーセリオ家は、いつか暴君の枷を外すことでしょう。今、ここでなくともね。きっと私に続く人がでる…敵が恐怖に震え上がらんことを！」
languages.original_text: "Tisiphone's heir be damned! I know that House Orsellio will cast off the tyrant's shackles someday, though not here and now. Others will come after me — and may our enemies tremble!"

traits.speaker: NaviRadicalLeader

languages.text: "Tisiphones Erbin soll verdammt sein! Ich weiß, dass das Haus Orsellio die Ketten der Tyrannin eines Tages abwerfen wird, wenn auch nicht hier und jetzt. Andere werden mir folgen – und unsere Feinde werden zittern!"
languages.original_text: "Tisiphone's heir be damned! I know that House Orsellio will cast off the tyrant's shackles someday, though not here and now. Others will come after me — and may our enemies tremble!"

languages.text: « Maudite soit l'héritière de Tisiphone ! Je sais que tôt ou tard, la maison Orsellio brisera les chaînes de la tyrannie. D'autres me succéderont, et alors nos ennemis trembleront ! »
languages.original_text: "Tisiphone's heir be damned! I know that House Orsellio will cast off the tyrant's shackles someday, though not here and now. Others will come after me — and may our enemies tremble!"

languages.text: "Tisiphone'nin vârisine lanet olsun! Belki bugün burada değil ama Orsellio Hanesi'nin bir gün tiranın zincirlerinden kurtulacağına eminim. Beni takip eden başkaları da olacaktır. Düşmanlarımız, karşımızda tir tir titresin!"

traits.speaker: NaviRadicalLeader
